    "caveat": "When operated in FIPS mode",
    "description": "The Seagate Secure® TCG Enterprise SSC FIPS 140 Module is embodied in Savvio®, Enterprise Performance®, Enterprise Turbo® and Constellation® model disk drives. These products meet the performance requirements of the most demanding Enterprise applications. The cryptographic module provides a wide range of cryptographic services using FIPS approved algorithms. Services include hardware-based data encryption, instant user data disposal with cryptographic erase, independently controlled and protected user data LBA bands and authenticated FW download.",
